channel.title: VAULT1 - didja miss me?
channel.description: I just posted a bunch of oldies and stuff I’ve been workshopping on my VAULT1 The Game page/new backup account. If you ever wanted more VAULT1 stuff then be sure to check that out! I just posted up 19 tracks, so there’s a super album for ya. https://m.soundcloud.com/vault1-the-game Again, thanks to everyone who’s been a part of my little auxy musical journey. VAULT1 has been a sweet project, so look forward to some extras every now and then!
